fr.istic.project.model.module.vcoa

Interface VCOA

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Caretaker, Module, ObservableModel
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JSynVCOA

    public interface VCOA
extends Module
    Defines the behavior of a VCOA Module.
    Invariant:
    getOscillatorType() != null, the frequency == REF_FREQUENCY * Math.pow(2, getOctave() + getFineTuning() + getVFm()), MIN_OCTAVE <= getOctave() <= MAX_OCTAVE
